    p.govuk-body
      | If a limit on the number of words or characters a user can enter is
        required, the <code>max_chars</code> and <code>max_words</code>
        parameters can be used. They provide feedback on how close the user is to
        the limit and automatically show an error if it is exceeeded.

  == render('/partials/example-fig.*',
