    p.govuk-body
      | If the limit is much higher than most users are likely to reach, you can
        choose to only display the message after a user has entered a certain
        amount.

    p.govuk-body
      | To do this, set the <code>threshold</code> parameter in conjunction with a word or
        character limit.

